<typeStatus box="[1326,1436,1062,1088]" pageId="11" pageNumber="24">Syntypes</typeStatus>
<number box="[151,166,1101,1127]" pageId="11" pageNumber="24" value="2.0">2</number>
ɗ (
<collectionCode box="[201,298,1101,1127]" pageId="11" pageNumber="24">BMNH</collectionCode>
)”. But only one male was found in the collection of the 
<collectionCode box="[955,1047,1101,1127]" pageId="11" pageNumber="24">BMNH</collectionCode>
. A 
<typeStatus box="[1087,1194,1101,1127]" pageId="11" pageNumber="24">lectotype</typeStatus>
is designated herein for 
<emphasis box="[192,312,1140,1165]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="24">P. o c e l l a t a</emphasis>
